ad" data-sbid="SB12423497912280243653204590088081736001528"></div><div class="articleBody" data-sbid="SB12423497912280243653204590088081736001528"><div class="clearfix bylineWrap"><time class="timestamp article__timestamp flexbox__flex--1">美国东部时间 2023 年 7 月 18 日上午 10:04 </time></div><div subscriptions-actions="" subscriptions-display="NOT data.noSharing"><div class="share-bar"><amp-social-share type="system" width="72" height="24" data-param-url="https://www.wsj.com/articles/china-taiwan-independence-dpp-lai-ching-te-b63b3b8c"></amp-social-share></div></div><section subscriptions-section="content"><div class="media-object scope-
